casebody.data:
State of TEXAS
v.
State of NEW MEXICO. No. 65, Original. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 5, 2018.

Motion of the River Master for fees and expenses is granted, and the River Master is awarded a total of $14,242.825, for the period July 1, 2017, through June 30, 2018, to be paid equally by the parties.
